column4: HomScent Lavender Pod Pourri, packaged by HomArt, is scented with a delicate fragrance of natural meadow and lavender flowers. HomArt’s HomScent Lavender Pod Pourri can be used alone as well as for sachets, or it can be combined with another Pod Pourri to create a personalized potpourri—with looks and fragrances to match unique tastes and decor! It can also be used to make wonderful homemade gifts, such as affordable but very personal and thoughtful homemade sachets or potpourri for special friends and associates on any gift-giving occasion. Or choose a votive cup, lantern, jar, or other container; add a candle; and use Lavender Pod Pourri as a base to add beautiful fragrance to the soft candlelight—also for a personal home decoration or as a lovely sophisticated homemade gift. The small bag of HomScent Lavender Pod Pourri is 5x3x5. For external use only; not suitable for foods or cooking.
